A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Code Section 5-3-10 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
2 manner for service of process, so as to provide for service by certified mail and statutory
3 overnight delivery, return receipt requested; to provide for related matters; to repeal
4 conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
5 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
6 SECTION 1.
7 Code Section 5-3-10 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to manner for
8 service of process, is amended in subsection (a) by revising paragraph (2), subparagraph
9 (a)(4)(C), and paragraphs (5) and (6) as follows:
10 "(2) Service of any document shall be made in person, by certified mail or statutory
11 overnight delivery, return receipt requested, or electronically if consent to electronic
12 service is given as provided in subsection (b) of this Code section;"
13 "(C) Read substantially as follows: 'I do certify that (number of copies) ____ (number
14 of copies) of the attached document(s) have been furnished to (name of party served)
15 ________________ (name of party served) by (delivery, mail, or email)
16 ________________ (delivery, certified mail, or statutory overnight delivery, return
